<div>
	<div style="margin-left:.25in;">Digi is in compliance with the general GST guidelines that identify which products and services are taxable under GST. They are as follows:</div>
	<div style="margin-left:.5in;">
		1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Discounts and promotional offers are subject to GST.</div>
	<div style="margin-left:.5in;">
		2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Effective 1 April 2015, rebates are classified as &ldquo;Offers&rdquo; or &ldquo;Discounts&rdquo;, and calculated as such. GST will be adjusted &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; accordingly.
	</div>
	<div style="margin-left:.5in;">
		3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Goods sold in Designated Areas (namely Labuan, Tioman and Langkawi) are exempt from GST.</div>
	<div style="margin-left:.5in;">&nbsp;</div>
